                <h1>Journalists discuss America&#039;s political polarization on eve of Trump inauguration</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/819d16a3-6c8b-4bca-b53b-38ecd0ed59d5.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;event&#x20;centered&#x20;around&#x20;clips&#x20;from&#x20;a&#x20;new&#x20;PBS&#x20;documentary,&#x20;&#x201C;Divided&#x20;States&#x20;of&#x20;America,&#x201D;&#x20;which&#x20;focuses&#x20;on&#x20;political&#x20;polarization.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The event centered around clips from a new PBS documentary, “Divided States of America,” which focuses on political polarization.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/neal-vaidya">Neal Vaidya</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/samantha-neal">Samantha Neal</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">January 20, 2017 | 12:14am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
